<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-11559] NPE when not setting a sampling interval on client subscriptions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-11559</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Due to an internal unintended auto-unboxing from &lt;tt&gt;Double&lt;/tt&gt; to &lt;tt&gt;double&lt;/tt&gt; milo may run into an NPE when the sampling interval is unset in the camel-milo component.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will provide a fix for this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
